## 2026-04-24 — Initial build complete

**What changed:** Full project scaffolded — customer flow, vendor flow, admin panel, mock mode.
**Why:** First deliverable.
**Files:** 73 files across src/ and supabase/migrations/. See PROJECT_BRIEF.md file map.
**Gotchas:**
- Activa 5G/4G 30-day pricing is seeded as `6499/4000km` (the rate card shows `40000km` which is suspected OCR typo). Verify with business before launch.
- Weekend override applies based on booking *start date*. If customer books Fri evening → Sun evening, they get weekday (Friday) pricing.
- In mock mode, everything is in-memory — no persistence across dev server restarts.